    "policy_language_limits_oversight_discipline": "Police Union Contract:\nAllows officers to overturn discipline through binding arbitration\nSection 29.4 An employee may appeal disciplinary actions taken under this ARTICLE under the provisions of ARTICLE 55 - GRIEVANCE GENERAL.",
