    "erases_misconduct_records": 1,
    "policy_language_erases_misconduct_records": "Police Union Contract:\nLetters of counseling are removed the personnel file after a period of 2-5 years.\nSection Article XIII. E. 3A. Letters of Counseling may be purged following a period of two (2) years from the date issued, except Letters of Counseling  resulting from a formal citizen's complaint will not be given consideration for purging until five (5) years from the date the Letter was issued.\n\nReprimands are purged from personnel file after a 5-year period.\nSection Article XIII. E. 3B. Letters of Reprimand may be purged following a period of five (5) years from the date the Letter was issued.",
