    "policy_language_has_use_of_force_continuum": "300.1 PURPOSE AND SCOPE\nThis policy provides guidelines on the reasonable use of force. While there is no way to specify the exact amount or type of reasonable force to be applied in any situation, every employee of this Department is expected to use these guidelines to make such decisions in a professional, impartial and reasonable manner.\n300.2 POLICY\nOfficers shall use only that amount of force that reasonably appears necessary given the facts and circumstances perceived by the officer at the time of the event to accomplish a legitimate law enforcement purpose.",
